// A second, unrelated private key — pairs with no certificate, so
// `listen_tls(TEST_CERT, MISMATCH_KEY)` is a genuine cert/key mismatch.
MISMATCH_KEY := "-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----
MIIEvQIBADANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQEFAASCBKcwggSjAgEAAoIBAQDQnsL7uR1mOuOv
